### Installing Ragie SDK with Bun

Source: https://github.com/ragieai/ragie-typescript/blob/main/README.md

This command installs the Ragie SDK using the Bun package manager, leveraging Bun's fast runtime and package management capabilities.

```bash
bun add ragie
```

--------------------------------

### Installing Ragie SDK with PNPM

Source: https://github.com/ragieai/ragie-typescript/blob/main/README.md

This command installs the Ragie SDK using the pnpm package manager, providing a disk-space efficient way to manage dependencies.

```bash
pnpm add ragie
```

