### Installing Ragie SDK with Yarn

Source: https://github.com/ragieai/ragie-typescript/blob/main/README.md

This command installs the Ragie SDK and its peer dependency 'zod' using the Yarn package manager, as Yarn does not automatically install peer dependencies.

```bash
yarn add ragie zod
```

