### Installing Ragie SDK with NPM

Source: https://github.com/ragieai/ragie-typescript/blob/main/README.md

This command installs the Ragie SDK using the npm package manager, making it available for use in your Node.js or TypeScript projects.

```bash
npm add ragie
```

