### Creating a Document with Ragie SDK

Source: https://github.com/ragieai/ragie-typescript/blob/main/README.md

This TypeScript example demonstrates how to initialize the Ragie SDK with an authentication token and then use it to create a document by uploading a file. It uses `node:fs` to open the file as a Blob.

```typescript
import { openAsBlob } from "node:fs";
import { Ragie } from "ragie";

const ragie = new Ragie({
  auth: "<YOUR_BEARER_TOKEN_HERE>",
});

async function run() {
  const result = await ragie.documents.create({
    file: await openAsBlob("example.file"),
  });

  // Handle the result
  console.log(result);
}

run();
```

